# Monitoring Rules

## Mandatory Prometheus metrics
- `{service}_requests_total{status,model_version}` (Counter)
- `{service}_request_duration_seconds` (Histogram)
- `{service}_prediction_score_bucket` (Histogram — C/C distribution)
- `{service}_model_info{version,commit}` (Gauge)
- `prediction_log_total` / `prediction_log_errors_total` (D-22)
- `{service}_performance_metric{slice_name,slice_value,metric}` (ADR-007)
- `{service}_psi_score{feature}` (ADR-006)
- `{service}_performance_last_run_timestamp` (heartbeat, D-09)
- Optional: `{service}_input_out_of_range_total{feature,direction}` (C4)

## Mandatory alerts (pair every alert with a heartbeat)
- GlobalAUCBelowAlert · SlicedAUCBelowAlert · PerformanceMonitorStale
  · PredictionLogErrorsHigh · SLOBurnRate · PSIBreach

## Grafana dashboards
- `dashboard-template.json` (basics) + `dashboard-closed-loop.json` (SLO/CC/drift)

## Invariants
- D-06 metric > 0.99 → investigate before alerting
- D-08 PSI uses QUANTILE bins, never uniform
- D-09 Every alert has a matching heartbeat alert
- D-22 Logger errors metered, never propagated to HTTP

See `.windsurf/rules/09-monitoring.md`, `13-closed-loop-monitoring.md`, ADR-006/007.
